msgctxt "1384"
msgid "Sassy Employee"
msgstr "Sassy Employee"

msgctxt "112_Sassy Employee"
msgid "Why, hello there, sweet thing! You make yourself at home now, mmkay?"
msgstr "Why, hello there, sweet thing! You make yourself at home now, mmkay?"

msgctxt "124_Sassy Employee"
msgid "Can't believe it's been a whole year since that big kerfuffle... Once the dust settled, I picked up a job here at this shop. I hope you'll come by sometime, you!"
msgstr "Can't believe it's been a whole year since that big kerfuffle... Once the dust settled, I picked up a job here at this shop. I hope you'll come by sometime, you!"

msgctxt "136_Sassy Employee"
msgid "Hey there, sweetie pie! ♥ You make yourself at home now, mmkay? ♥"
msgstr "Hey there, sweetie pie! ♥ You make yourself at home now, mmkay? ♥"

msgctxt "148_Sassy Employee"
msgid "Oh, hey there! You make yourself at home now, mmkay? ♥"
msgstr "Oh, hey there! You make yourself at home now, mmkay? ♥"

msgctxt "160_Sassy Employee"
msgid "I'm Michiru. Just started here the other day! Hope you'll stop by sometime, sugar! ♥"
msgstr "I'm Michiru. Just started here the other day! Hope you'll stop by sometime, sugar! ♥"

